data.description: Beautiful house on a 1+ acre lot in Emerald Forest! Close to McDonough, Locust Grove, I-75, and Griffin. Enter this home to a gracious foyer with formal dining to the left and a light-filled living room ahead. This split bedroom plan features a primary suite with a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, soaking tub with jets, separate shower, and double vanity. Two additional bedrooms with shared full baths are located on the other side of the home, offering privacy. There is a 4th bedroom located upstairs - perfect for a teen bedroom, playroom, or office. The kitchen features updated cabinets, a pantry, is open to the breakfast area, and a large family room with a fireplace. This area leads to a large deck and fenced backyard. Large lot, park in neighborhood, 4 bedrooms, living room AND family room, deck, fenced backyard - this home has it all! HVAC was replaced within the last 12 months. A must-see!
